theorem Topology.closure_eq_interior_union_frontier {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    (A : Set X) :
    closure (A : Set X) = interior A ∪ frontier (A : Set X) := by
  ext x
  constructor
  · intro hxCl
    by_cases hxInt : x ∈ interior A
    · exact Or.inl hxInt
    · have hxFrontier : x ∈ frontier (A : Set X) := by
        exact And.intro hxCl hxInt
      exact Or.inr hxFrontier
  · intro hx
    cases hx with
    | inl hxInt =>
        exact interior_subset hxInt
    | inr hxFrontier =>
        exact hxFrontier.1
